title: Talking Taylor: Red (Taylor's Version)
description:
Today we're recapping the biggest album of the year: RED (TAYLOR'S VERSION!) We talk about the 10 minute version, our favorite songs from the vault, Shmake Shmyllenhall (IYKYK) and of course play some games and learn some trivia. Was this re release everything you were hoping it would be?!
